https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/
Windows: https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/installer/
Minimal requirement Installation: Select SqlServer + Connector/J + MySQL Workbench

1. Setup MySQL Server
2. Create database schema and its tables (check ddl directory for queries)
3. Create a Java application with will:
    a. Connect to a MySQL schema
    b. INSERT a new employee and get it assigned to the "Employee AI" project
    c. UPDATE department of Maria to "IT"
    d. DELETE project "Employee manager app"
    c. SELECT all employees that work on project "Instant payment app"

Note: Each CRUD operation will be a method and the parameters will be used in the PreparedStatements